<ul><li><a href="//slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=25551&amp;threshold=1&amp;commentsort=0&amp;mode=thread&amp;pid=2775995#2814213">Re:Definitions of terms</a> by Scott Warner (Score:1) Wednesday January 09, @10:05PM
